data.description: This darling 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home offers a blend of comfort and style. Inside, discover a bright open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the living spaces. The dinning area, conveniently located within the kitchen, is the ideal space for entertaining. The inviting living room, featuring a cozy wood-burning fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. The primary bedroom boasting not only comfort but also functionality with its walk-in closets, provides ample storage space. The additional two bedrooms are generously sized, offering versatility for guest rooms, home office, or hobbies. Enjoy a fenced in backyard just waiting to be made into an oasis for entertaining or enjoying a relaxing morning coffee. HVAC was serviced this year. New roof added 2023. Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your home! **Sellers are offering 10K at closing to be used toward closing costs or buy down of points.**
